Cooked perch
Type: Consumable
Value: 1
Fine Value: 11
Keywords: Cooked fish
Food
Search
Keyword: 		Crafting
Duration: 500 steps
Properties:
Bankable:     Droppable:
Sellable:     Tradable:

Pan-fried or grilled, cooked perch offers a delightful flakiness and a mild, slightly sweet taste. Perfect for a light meal.

The Cooked perch item is a consumable.

Attributes

Quality Attributes

+2% Work efficiency While doing Crafting.

+4% Work efficiency While doing Crafting.

Uses

This item may be consumed for a temporary buff.
